data.name: NFTShiba.Finance
data.description:
1.	What is NFTShiba.Finance Protocol(NFTSHIBA)?

NFTSHIBA uses BSC Decentralized blockchain code.
It can trade on pancakeswap V2 and listing on it. NFTSHIBA Protocol will be a system 
where anyone can have fun and participate like a game and even invest. 
Art Gallery, Artist, and Invester three forms an ecosystem, and it is a system that automatically moves Fees using NFTPUNK as a currency.
Our team was formed on March 2021, and it was launched on 15:00 June 11th (UTC).
NFTSHIBA Finance focuses on new concepts and NFT Virtual Game.
NFTSHIBA's NFT contsins Art Gallery that will have its own central agency to proof NFT itself.
 



2.	NFTPUNK is native utility token that is used for

There will be 10% of fee to the investers making transactions. (5% holder, 4% Liquidity) 
All the fees will be sent to the holders, when buying and selling Art NFT from platform.
All the fees will be disperse into both sides of Art Gallery, investers, and artists.

3. Do you know how many NFTSHIBA tokens are distributed?

NFTSHIBA protocol tokens were created on June 11tht, 2021 by BEP20.
50% progressed Burn, 5% from development team, 45% of liquidity was provided to the market.
During 45%+5%transaction volume 10%(5%holder+4%Liquidity) fee will be charged to all the holders.
1/holders transaction volume will be forever Burn.
Scarcity of NFTPUNK will reach higher as the time goes by.

4. Who are the founders of NFTSHIBA Protocol?

NFTSHIBA is an idea from Tetsuya Saito, it was to secure the previous NFT 2.O serious problems.
His experience in programming is amazing and has great talent for business. He realized the problems and bubbles from previous NFT Art. 
NFT Art believed that there should be a reliable central agency because of NFT Art system that could infringe copyright of picture itself  and continue to duplicate NFT itself.

5. Where can I buy NFTSHIBA Protocol? (NFTSHIBA)?

NFTSHIBA is base of BEP20 and provides liquidity for BNB, which can be purchased with all the tokens and coins paired with BNB in a PancakeSwapV2 and IndoEX Exchange.
Purchases can be made by liquidity from June 11th, 2021 at BEP20 based PancakeSwapV2, and can be made after setting the transaction fee of slippage 10%.

6. ‘The Punk&SHIBA World’ (NFT Virtual gallery game)

' THE PUNK&SHIBA WORLD ' is NFT game.
It's Pixel Virtual world is similar with Minecraft. By accessing this program,
you can inter the Tokyo art gallery without visiting Tokyo.
The virtual world will be same as the actual Tokyo art gallery.
You can monitor public art, Locked Art from here and also able to purchase it.
There will be a fee occurring to tjis transaction, this fee will be distributed to holder
and artist fee, and art gallery fee.
